---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Pathfinding — plan a trip in plain language"
  description="Pathfinding is an AI trip planner: chat to build an itinerary, see your days on the map, and keep every trip in one place."
>
  <h1>Pathfinding</h1>
  <p class="tagline">Plan a trip in plain language. Chat with an AI planner and see it on the map.</p>

  <ul class="features">
    <li><strong>Chat to plan</strong>
        <span>Tell Pathfinding where and when; get a day-by-day plan you can edit.</span></li>
    <li><strong>Itinerary, mapped</strong>
        <span>Every stop and every day, organized and laid out on the map.</span></li>
    <li><strong>All your trips</strong>
        <span>Past, current, and upcoming trips kept in one place.</span></li>
    <li><strong>Guest or synced</strong>
        <span>Plan as a guest, or sign in to sync your trips across devices.</span></li>
  </ul>

  <span class="badge">Coming soon to the App Store</span>

  <footer>
    <a href="/pathfinding/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a> · <a href="/pathfinding/support/">Support</a>
  </footer>
</Base>
